data.description: This charming brick ranch home sits on a huge 1.35-acre lot in Gilbert! There's much to love about this home, including a newer roof! The large front porch welcomes you to sit & enjoy the peaceful lot. Upon entry, you are greeted by luxury vinyl plank floors & tall smooth ceilings. The open floor plan allows natural light to flow through the home. The formal living room features a wood burning fireplace w/ built-in shelving on each side. The great room is complemented by beautiful shelf molding that can be used for endless purposes. The kitchen boasts recessed lighting, ample cabinet space, granite countertops, tile flooring, stainless steel appliances & the opportunity for a charming breakfast nook w/ a bay window! The master bedroom provides you w/ plenty of closet space & offers an en-suite bathroom w/ updated flooring, a dual vanity, and a tub/shower combo. A spacious screened-in back porch creates a delightful private outdoor living space, & a mudroom keeps everything tidy. If you need an office or craft room there is a flex room for it all! The attached carport provides covered parking, or a covered area to grill out w/ friends. There is a storage room for all of your yard tools & toys. This home is zoned for Gilbert school & located 30 minutes from downtown Columbia, where you will find tons of shopping & dining options. Come see this home today! **Seller is offering a flooring & tub refinish allowance w/ an acceptable offer & as part of the sales contract.**
